{"tid":20605,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的今日撞到女神","createTime":"2016-12-03T12:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T02:46:40.000Z","uid":9601,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdced602c1f90d5097583e3bd8f900f1e51f9048","tid":20605,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"「起身啦衰仔，成日都唔知醒返學。」<br />\n<br />\n聽到依句我就即刻彈左起身，你以為我係比我媽子大叫聲吵醒？你錯啦，我係比佢放係我頭上雪過濕毛巾整醒，仲要係冬天，唉....<br />\n<br />\n我用九秒八七速度換衫拎住媽子整好嘅三文治衝左出門口。點解係九秒八七？因為我係異於常人，九秒九每個人都可以做到，實在太垃圾。哈！<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我叫陳子樂，係一個普普通通既中五生。仆街唔記得帶書包。<br />\n<br />\n「陳子樂，你今日係就係冇遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但你個書包呢？」佢就係我班主任<br />\n<br />\n「上次你就PE衫加皮鞋，今次你就唔就得帶書包，你個腦去左邊？姐係欠交功課啦，今日留堂罰抄。」<br />\n<br />\n「咪去左屎忽到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」佢就係我老死，李魯明。<br />\n<br />\n「我..唉」<br />\n<br />\n突然有一股仙氣漂過<br />\n<br />\n「嘩女神啊」成班都係冇用嘅垃圾兵仔。<br />\n<br />\n「啤咩啊？死臭雞」我當然冇講出口，其實佢都係我女神。唉<br />\n<br />\n「無驚無險又到六點，留完堂走人，miss 88。」我好快就衝左出去<br />\n<br />\n就係轉角位撞到女神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點算好？女神比我撞到飛左落樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求救，我冇錢賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（開錯左係吹水堂，對唔住某位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"2b8f10f4200c7796ec9054ebcb6c2423892942a6","tid":20605,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75dd8c08fde03c7f6a9435e383be58332a271bc","tid":20605,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5398674f2033b1f3dd7b4b82677aade8d66219d3","tid":20605,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:28:08.000Z","msg":"仲以為係故添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27462211a643ed77f98f68d8df24cf3430013c9e","tid":20605,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:34:17.000Z","msg":"屌都估到係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd665e7843ad725af132002ca1dcc29dea704aa7","tid":20605,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"求救緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">終於有兩位巴打理我 又中左伏 好開心　</span></span>"}]}